{"tid":689161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(台灣)民進黨立委: 忘記「六四」是自我催眠, 等待天朝恩賞","createTime":"2018-06-04T01:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T02:51:11.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac7e36da779aefee21c52dfe6299b639074d218","tid":689161,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2446758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446758&d=vzNaOYh9vM3wKlqSaL%2BMtr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=fa7d663e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446758&h=6d968408\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2446758</a><br />\n<br />\n「有人選擇忘記」 段宜康藉六四諷刺「這些台灣人」 <br />\n2018-06-04 09:05<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕今日是中國六四事件29週年，世界各地皆有人權團體舉辦悼念活動，民進黨立委段宜康也在臉書發表看法，從六四看近期台灣時事發展，段宜康表示，有些台灣人，動不動就搬出五四，但拒絕記得八九（中國八九學運）六四，而且絶不會放棄九二共識。<br />\n<br />\n段宜康指出，中國人之所以遺忘八九民運，是因為極權政府鋪天蓋地的封鎖；<strong>但有一部分台灣人「選擇」忘記六四，閉上眼睛用「只掃門前雪的自我催眠」，繼續等待天朝的恩賞</strong>。隨後段宜康則說，這些台灣人在我國因為中國因素的外交挫敗時，回頭指責自己的政府，這種邏輯就好像把天安門事件的責任，推到29年前的北京市民和大學生頭上一樣。<br />\n<br />\n最後段宜康則諷刺地說：「這些台灣人，動不動就搬出五四；可拒絕記得八九六四；而且絶不會放棄九二共識。」"},{"pid":"6c271431c46cf522fecf97db69071480d4345e69","tid":689161,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161affc93494e64049a901f0ab1f991cbc5b4ced","tid":689161,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:21:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港成班冚家挪住外國護照既大愛支，仲要班後生燒多幾多青春，去為一個一早燈紅酒綠紙醉金迷既遠方城市哭喪自瀆？？？</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>當年中國64<br />\n如果無香港人傷亡<br />\n香港駛唔駛年年攪咁多活動悼念<br />\n全球無一個地方好似香港大陣象</blockquote>大中華膠多 個時好多都對中國有幻想有希望</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要悼念，班大愛支係咪最應該為六四後仲支持民主回西路樓死先呢？？？尤其個班之後冚家攞定護照走既！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2f3f96a542c682d0961f34db1c0879a713b58492","tid":689161,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bce1e4261e7c1ff65f3cc207c7125cef003a56","tid":689161,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d34d4b8d2b4cb71b4d1b201e45d25a57adf7dd","tid":689161,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b55c9f0f10ca2d488db99a163188e95c9cc9f4d","tid":689161,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98e3006ed026a86fc18ba9bb5e6ca7e7919f024","tid":689161,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}